text.tspan: This includes collecting data from devices through physical, logical, and cloud-based
acquisition methods. Physical acquisition entails making a bit-by-bit copy of the device's
storage, capturing all data, including deleted files. Logical acquisition extracts data through the
device's operating system, while cloud-based acquisition gets data from services like Google
Once data is acquired, it is parsed to extract legible information. WhatsApp stores messages
and metadata in databases (e.g., msgstore.db), which require specialist tools to parse. Analysis
includes reviewing messages, timestamps, contact lists, and multimedia files to find trends,
relationships, and other pertinent information (Chowdhury et al., 2022).
